Module ui
Package engine.bot.rule_based_old

Class CheckCollisionAndHeight

java.lang.Object
engine.bot.rule_based_old.CheckCollisionAndHeight
public class CheckCollisionAndHeight extends Object
This class is responsible for checking collisions and height differences for the Bot's decision-making process. It uses the RungeKutta4Void solver to simulate the physics of the golf ball.
